  "description": "Name variants for two arms: (A) token-exact paired resumes where the name is HELD FIXED within a treatment/control pair and varied across replicates; (B) pairwise candidate-choice where two candidates need distinct, demographically-matched names. matched_name_group lets the pairwise task pick two names that share gender (and race-coding) so the name is not confounded with the identity signal unless a condition explicitly varies it. token_count is computed at generation time by the exact tokenizer.",
